"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:16:49.000Z","msg":"已經不意外<br />\n以前就話小學生講普通話 再過幾年就成街中學生講普通話<br />\n前幾日我喺中環返工 出去食lunch 成堆著住西裝嘅蝗 一路行返公司一路講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港已死"},{"pid":"398b8d50b38ea66002b881ba18a36a2090b65669","tid":1040463,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26e04782989089c20d6a92128326cbd957c2637e","tid":1040463,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"東同辦冇用殘體<br />\n應該唔係中國人寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"你教書嗰陣有冇繁簡夾雜咁寫"},{"pid":"06ec8d7cf167d368dfc5d070b370e443dc3a1552","tid":1040463,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"你地仲以為呢個政府仲係真正嘅香港人主政啊"},{"pid":"70ea9f9c4f251408c832a8b56ebd82a08320c348","tid":1040463,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"窿窿罅罅都滲透曬啦"},{"pid":"24ee77daa26b3fc5ed2c4c8ca7ef9403b111111d","tid":1040463,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T07:28:24.000Z","msg":"雜种公涵"},{"pid":"3981b4a9e8daacdf0aa1699d010030b38927ff4e","tid":1040463,"uid":12704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc96ef33394aa65a9a0cc28a2f94912c28f89793","tid":1040463,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"點解會手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釣魚信嚟㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"我收過入境處嘅信都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340dcfe6f4f9d17082b75afc94cca4579ee24f4d","tid":1040463,"uid":36494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"九成請咗支那新移民啦"},{"pid":"4e2efa4988b25eb41849c1ec18d759ac01adf244","tid":1040463,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img s